OL,3,CFifth MP calls on Andy Burnham to
OL,4,Cintroduce free bus pass for homeless
OL,5,Cchildren
OL,7,FA fifth MP has called on Mayor Andy
OL,8,FBurnham to introduce a free bus pass
OL,9,Ffor children in temporary
OL,10,Faccommodation.
OL,12,FLisa Smart, Liberal Democrat MP for
OL,13,FHazel Grove, is the latest figure to
OL,14,Fcall for the scheme to be introduced
OL,15,Fin Greater Manchester, as the number
OL,16,Fof homeless children continues to rise.
