OL,3,CFifth MP calls on Andy Burnham to
OL,4,Cintroduce free bus pass for homeless
OL,5,Cchildren
OL,7,FExperts from a number of not-for-
OL,8,Fprofit groups say children in
OL,9,Ftemporary accommodation are often
OL,10,Fmoved miles away from their home,
OL,11,Fmeaning they have to take multiple
OL,12,Fbuses to reach a school that was
OL,13,Fpreviously within walking distance.
OL,15,FCouncil rules say children can only
OL,16,Fget free transport if they move more
OL,17,Fthan two miles from home and there is
OL,18,Fno "suitable school" nearer, but
OL,19,Fcampaigners say a sudden change to a
OL,20,Fchild's learning environment can
OL,21,Fdisrupt their education.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
