OL,3,CFifth MP calls on Andy Burnham to
OL,4,Cintroduce free bus pass for homeless
OL,5,Cchildren
OL,7,FLisa Smart said: "One of my earliest
OL,8,Fcases as an MP was getting a bus pass
OL,9,Ffor a child who was having to walk
OL,10,Fmiles to and from school every day,
OL,11,Fbecause of where he and his mother had
OL,12,Fbeen forced to move to.
OL,14,F"Children should never suffer in these
OL,15,Fcircumstances, and this is a great
OL,16,Fcampaign to remove one of those
OL,17,Fbarriers.
OL,26,@oD@ROUvD@AOU
