OL,3,CFifth MP calls on Andy Burnham to
OL,4,Cintroduce free bus pass for homeless
OL,5,Cchildren
OL,7,F"There are simply too many challenges
OL,8,Ffor young people in difficult
OL,9,Fcircumstances, as we see in the
OL,10,Fpressures on budgets for children with
OL,11,Fspecial educational needs."
OL,13,FLisa Smart is the fifth MP to back the
OL,14,Fcampaign, alongside fellow Stockport
OL,15,FLib Dem MP Tom Morrison, who
OL,16,Frepresents Cheadle, and a trio of
OL,17,FLabour figures: Salford's Rebecca Long-
OL,18,FBailey, Bury South's Christian
OL,19,FWakeford, and Yasmin Qureshi for
OL,20,FBolton South and Walkden.
