OL,3,CFifth MP calls on Andy Burnham to
OL,4,Cintroduce free bus pass for homeless
OL,5,Cchildren
OL,7,FThey join three major not-for-profits,
OL,8,FResolve Poverty, Wood Street Mission,
OL,9,Fand Shared Health.
OL,11,FIn repsonse, a mayoral spokesperson
OL,12,Fsaid: "We are doing a lot to make
OL,13,Ftravel easier and more affordable for
OL,14,Feveryone in Greater Manchester,
OL,15,Fincluding children and young adults.
OL,17,F"That includes #1 single bus fares,
OL,18,Ffree travel for 16-18-year-olds, an
OL,19,Fextension of free travel for care
OL,20,Fleavers and, from next month, half
OL,21,Fprice bus travel for 18-21-year-olds.
OL,26,@tD@GOU
