OL,7,F"Transport for Greater Manchester is
OL,8,Fcurrently undertaking a broader review
OL,9,Fof concessions, considering all the
OL,10,Frequests for support that we get from
OL,11,Fa range of groups across the city-
OL,12,Fregion, and the Mayor has asked them
OL,13,Fto ensure this is included."
